This just in- You, in the kitchen. You decide to start listing off everything you see in the room, as if you were in a text adventure.

What's that over there? It looks like it's a fridge. The fridge is empty, what a horrible day! You make out an oven. You idly wonder how they came up with the name TextWorld for this place. It's pretty fitting. You can make out a table. The table is massive. On the table you can make out a knife. Were you looking for a counter? Because look over there, it's a counter. On the counter you make out a cookbook. You see a stove. Unfortunately, there isn't a thing on it.

There is an open plain door leading west. There is an exit to the east. Don't worry, there is no door. There is an exit to the north. Don't worry, there is no door.
